    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_14107-14191",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14107-14191",
      "markText": "我在这繁响的拥抱中，也懒散而且舒适，从白天以至初夜的疑虑，全给祝福的空气一扫而空了，只觉得天地圣众歆享了牲醴和香烟，都醉醺醺的在空中蹒跚，豫备给鲁镇的人们以无限的幸福。",
      "totalCount": 2125,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14107&rangeEnd=14191",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14107&rangeEnd=14191"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_9_6679-6752",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6679-6752",
      "markText": "他看见眼前浮出一朵扁圆的乌花，橙黄心，从左眼的左角漂到右，消失了；接着一朵明绿花，墨绿色的心；接着一座六株的白菜堆，屹然的向他叠成一个很大的A字。",
      "totalCount": 1190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6679&rangeEnd=6752",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6679&rangeEnd=6752"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_3441-3518",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3441-3518",
      "markText": "“说不清”是一句极有用的话。不更事的勇敢的少年，往往敢于给人解决疑问，选定医生，万一结果不佳，大抵反成了怨府，然而一用这说不清来作结束，便事事逍遥自在了。",
      "totalCount": 1188,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3441&rangeEnd=3518",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3441&rangeEnd=3518"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_8_1462-1521",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1462-1521",
      "markText": "觉得北方固不是我的旧乡，但南来又只能算一个客子，无论那边的干雪怎样纷飞，这里的柔雪又怎样的依恋，于我都没有什么关系了。",
      "totalCount": 1100,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1462&rangeEnd=1521",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1462&rangeEnd=1521"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_15_15494-15577",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "15494-15577",
      "markText": "我愿意真有所谓鬼魂，真有所谓地狱，那么，即使在孽风怒吼之中，我也将寻觅子君，当面说出我的悔恨和悲哀，祈求她的饶恕；否则，地狱的毒焰将围绕我，猛烈地烧尽我的悔恨和悲哀。",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15494&rangeEnd=15577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15494&rangeEnd=15577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_8_2807-2898",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2807-2898",
      "markText": "我在少年时，看见蜂子或蝇子停在一个地方，给什么来一吓，即刻飞去了，但是飞了一个小圈子，便又回来停在原地点，便以为这实在很可笑，也可怜。可不料现在我自己也飞回来了，不过绕了一点小圈子。",
      "totalCount": 1003,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2807&rangeEnd=2898",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2807&rangeEnd=2898"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_1421-1441",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1421-1441",
      "markText": "拜的却只限于男人，拜完自然仍然是放爆竹。",
      "totalCount": 930,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1421&rangeEnd=1441",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1421&rangeEnd=1441"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_10711-10792",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10711-10792",
      "markText": "有些老女人没有在街头听到她的话，便特意寻来，要听她这一段悲惨的故事。直到她说到呜咽，她们也就一齐流下那停在眼角上的眼泪，叹息一番，满足的去了，一面还纷纷的评论着。",
      "totalCount": 902,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10711&rangeEnd=10792",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10711&rangeEnd=10792"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_10_7113-7189",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7113-7189",
      "markText": "“我们女人怎么样？我们女人，比你们男人好得多。你们男人不是骂十八九岁的女学生，就是称赞十八九岁的女讨饭：都不是什么好心思。‘咯支咯支’，简直是不要脸！”",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7113&rangeEnd=7189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7113&rangeEnd=7189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_15_15882-15933",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "15882-15933",
      "markText": "我要向着新的生路跨进第一步去，我要将真实深深地藏在心的创伤中，默默地前行，用遗忘和说谎做我的前导……。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15882&rangeEnd=15933",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=15882&rangeEnd=15933"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_11400-11485",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "11400-11485",
      "markText": "她未必知道她的悲哀经大家咀嚼赏鉴了许多天，早已成为渣滓，只值得烦厌和唾弃；但从人们的笑影上，也仿佛觉得这又冷又尖，自己再没有开口的必要了。她单是一瞥他们，并不回答一句话。",
      "totalCount": 800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11400&rangeEnd=11485",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=11400&rangeEnd=11485"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_8_5504-5590",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5504-5590",
      "markText": "然而我毫不抱怨，因为她过来收拾空碗时候的忍着的得意的笑容，已尽够赔偿我的苦痛而有余了。所以我这一夜虽然饱胀得睡不稳，又做了一大串恶梦，也还是祝赞她一生幸福，愿世界为她变好。",
      "totalCount": 748,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5504&rangeEnd=5590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5504&rangeEnd=5590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_3762-3808",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3762-3808",
      "markText": "我因为常见些但愿不如所料，以为未必竟如所料的事，却每每恰如所料的起来，所以很恐怕这事也一律。",
      "totalCount": 741,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3762&rangeEnd=3808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3762&rangeEnd=3808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_7_12334-12434",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "12334-12434",
      "markText": "柳妈诡秘的说。“再一强，或者索性撞一个死，就好了。现在呢，你和你的第二个男人过活不到两年，倒落了一件大罪名。你想，你将来到阴司去，那两个死鬼的男人还要争，你给了谁好呢？阎罗大王只好把你锯开来，分给他们",
      "totalCount": 732,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12334&rangeEnd=12434",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12334&rangeEnd=12434"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_15_8959-9030",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "8959-9030",
      "markText": "待到孤身枯坐，回忆从前，这才觉得大半年来，只为了爱，——盲目的爱，——而将别的人生的要义全盘疏忽了。第一，便是生活。人必生活着，爱才有所附丽。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=43211836&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8959&rangeEnd=9030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/cae324a072935c3ccaee908?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8959&rangeEnd=9030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "43211836_15_10874-10958",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "10874-10958",
      "markText": "“……况且你已经可以无须顾虑，勇往直前了。你要我老实说；是的，人是不该虚伪的。我老实说罢：因为，因为我已经不爱你了！但这于你倒好得多，因为你更可以毫无挂念地做事……。”",
